headline: Deutsche Bank backs Visa, Mastercard amid fintech sector slump
summary: Investing.com -- Deutsche Bank resumed coverage on payments and IT services stocks, with preference for high-quality fintech names like Visa (NYSE:V), Mastercard (NYSE:MA), even as the broader sector continues to underperform the S&P 500 this year.
